# Mayo - for Strava

Mayo integrates with the Strava API to help athletes discover their most common routes across running, cycling, touring and other sports.
By grouping and visualizing activities, the app generates a personalized heatmap that highlights frequently used paths and training patterns.

## Features
- View personal Strava activities pulled directly from the API
- Route grouping to identify commonly used paths
- Automated creation of a personal heatmap based on activities
- Supports multiple activity types

## Tech Stack

- Vercel Serverless Functions for OAuth
- Strava API
- Bootstrap
- Leaflet
- mapbox polyline
